pageContext.claim: “But President Obama, after years and years and years, they said, ‘We're not going to approve it.’ I said, ‘We'll approve it.’ Forty-eight thousand jobs. Think of it. It's being built right now. They're both being built. One just got completed -- Dakota Access.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump signed an executive order to expedite completion of the Dakota Access Pipeline. But much of that pipeline was built during the Obama administration.
